Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:48.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}为将你守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:52.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我甘愿奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:58.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:12.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}苍焰是为使两人邂逅的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:17.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将频频闪现的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:22.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}照耀得鲜明活现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:26.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}纵有天负伤倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:30.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也终要在我怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:35.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}安详地沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:41.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}紧拥着坚定信念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:46.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}追随之心将不受时空的阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:52.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只愿你放出慑人光芒的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:59.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}会映有我的身影
